Those portions are non-commercial only.

This repository designates only the C6-derived Gen 5 additions as subject to
the FASL. Earlier OpenHaldex-S3 work authored independently before the
March 4, 2026 introduction of the public C6 FASL is not reclassified by this
notice.

If you redistribute source or binaries that include the Gen 5 / C6-derived
portions, you must preserve the applicable notices and include the FASL text.

